{
  "id": "adv_card_chs_53_01",
  "title": "白石千紗 1話 10カワだよ",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――十一月二十二日　朝",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "うん、うまく出来たかも。怜ちゃんから見て\nどうだった？　直した方がいい箇所とか、あったかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "特にないわよ。そもそも私が今の千紗に教えられること\nなんてないわ。あっても個人的な意見を言うくらいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ～、それ何度か言ってくれてるけど、怜ちゃんに\n比べたら、私まだまだだよ？　もっと習いたいよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ千紗は、莉央さんのご飯と遙子さんのご飯\nどっちの方が美味しいと思う？　比べられないでしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "千紗のダンスは、もうそのレベルってこと\n私と比べても遜色ないし、もう好みのレベルだわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それは言い過ぎかもだけど、そっか、怜ちゃんからは\nそう見えるんだね。私には、私の色や味があるんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "えぇ、基礎はバッチリ。今後は今まで以上に自分なりの\n表現を伸ばせるといいわね。まぁそれが難しいんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、教えることはなくても、アドバイスは出来るから\nもし悩むことがあったら、いつでも相談に乗るわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "うん！　怜ちゃん、ありがとう\n早起き苦手なのに、自主練にも付き合ってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "まぁ、その、千紗の誕生日だし？\nついでに、プレゼントをあげようと思って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "じ、実は、千紗のために怖い話を考えてきたのよ\n大体の話は知ってるだろうから、こう、頑張って自分で",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "怜ちゃんのオリジナル……！？　フィクションだって\n言っちゃってるけど……聞いてみたい……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.5333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 14099.999999999995,
          "startTime": 124.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-01.m4a",
          "delay": 16099.999999999995,
          "startTime": 126.6333333333
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-04.m4a",
          "delay": 28533.3315532,
          "startTime": 139.0666648865
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.2833315532
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 115.5333315532
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 124.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "こほん。これは私が友達の友達から聞いた話なんだけど\n夜遅く歩いていたら、偶然タクシーが通りかかってね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "友達の友達……さっき、自分で考えたって\n言っちゃってたけど……うん、それで？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.2,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_car-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8266.666666700019,
          "startTime": 143.4666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 139.0666648865
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 144.8
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "もう遅いし、家まで乗っていこうとタクシーを止めたの\nでも運転手さんが不気味で、妙にエアコンも効いてて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 150.9999982198
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "嫌だなー、寒いなーって思いながら乗ってたら\n急に運転手さんが話し掛けてきたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 155.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 159.3333315532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "「このあたりで、さっき事故が起きたんですよ\n一人、亡くなってしまったみたいで」って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 163.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 167.2333315532
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "そして、振り返ってこう言ったの。「それは」……\n「お前だーーーーーーーーーー！！」",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 173.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_countryroad-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "countryroad-00-night",
      "startTime": 173.7
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_lesson-01-000-noon",
      "startTime": 177.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "っ……凄い！　古典的だけど、それっぽくなってるよ！\n怜ちゃんが考えたんだよね！？　凄い凄い！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 184.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei013.m4a",
      "text": "な、なんなのよその反応。全然怖がってないし\nはぁ、これじゃあ、せいぜい1怖ってとこかしら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 193.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa Shiraishi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　良かったよ？　怜ちゃんらしい色が出てたし\n頑張って考えてくれたんだなって思うと、10カワだよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 202.9666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 12099.999999999995,
          "startTime": 215.0666666667
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei Ichinose",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_01-rei014.m4a",
      "text": "10怖じゃなくて10カワ？　もしかして、可愛いって\n意味じゃ……あ、待ちなさい、今のいじってたわよね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 213.9,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}